            <h4>A birdwatcher</h4>
            <hr />
            <h4>Keep a record of your bird sightings with Birder:</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Organise your observations into categories with tags <i>(coming up soon)</i></li>
                <li>Upload photographs of the birds you spotted <i>(coming up soon)</i></li>
            </ul>

            <br />
            <h4>Build a network of like-minded bird lovers:</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>View and comment on observations from users you follow <i>(coming up soon)</i></li>
            </ul>

            <br />
            <h4>Log your observations in the field:</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>With the Android and iOS apps <i>(coming up soon)</i></li>
            </ul>

            <br />
            <h4>Images:</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Retrieve and display an image from database</i></li>
            </ul>

